name: Orbits.
body:
3 VERTICES
***

Give rise to 4-dimensional polytope in 6 dimensions.   
21 Faces, 42 edges, 22 vertices.   
(3 extruded triangles and 3 extruded quadrangles.)   


Polygon 1.   
` Parameter  A = 0.8  |  B = 1.2`   

Polygon 2.   
` Parameter  A = 0.8  |  B = 1.2 `   

Polygon 3.   
` Parameter  A = 0.7  |  B = 1.1 `   

Polygon 4.   
` Parameter  A = 0.5  |  B = 1.9 `   

Polygon 5.   
` Parameter  A = 0.8  |  B = 1.2 `   


   




4 VERTICES
***   

Give rise to 5-dimensional polytope in 8 dimensions.   
(Approx. 83 Faces, 153 edges, 126 vertices.)  





5 DIMENSIONS
***   

Give rise to 6-dimensional polytope in 10 dimensions.   


   



6 DIMENSIONS
***   

Give rise to some polytope in 12 dimensions.  
Only the pictures.



Other things to follow.
